1 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY Section 7, Chapter 291, O.S.L.
2 2023 (70 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 6-104.9), is amended to read as
3 follows:
4 Section 6-104.9. A. There is hereby created in the State
5 Treasury a revolving fund for the State Board of Education to be
6 designated the “Public School Paid Maternity Leave Revolving Fund”.
7 The fund shall be a continuing fund, not subject to fiscal year
8 limitations, and shall consist of all monies received by the State
9 Board of Education from state appropriations provided for the
(Floor Amendments Only) Date and Time Filed:
