1 purposes set forth in Sections 6-104 and 6-104.8 of this title.
2 All monies accruing to the credit of the fund are hereby
3 appropriated and may be budgeted and expended by the State Board of
4 Education for the purpose of reimbursing school districts for
5 expenses related to providing paid maternity and bereavement leave
6 as provided for in subsection B of this section. Expenditures from
7 the fund shall be made upon warrants issued by the State Treasurer
8 against claims filed as prescribed by law with the Director of the
9 Office of Management and Enterprise Services for approval and
10 payment.
11 B. School districts in this state shall file claims with the
12 State Board of Education for reimbursement of expenses related to
13 providing eligible employees with paid maternity leave as provided
14 for in Section 1 6-104.8 of this act title and paid bereavement
15 leave as provided for in Section 6-104 of this title.
